game.name: Jellyfish
game.description:
Are you a lover of jellyfish? Is it your dream of living a life of a cute and lovely jellyfish and explore the mystery deep sea? If your answer is yes for the both the questions, we have got you covered with a brand new adventure challenge where you will get a chance to make your dream come in a colorful environment. Join Jellyfish game and get ready to discover the underwater world in your own style!
Your objective in this cool html5 fish game is to help your jellyfish to reach to the top while avoiding all the deadly obstacles. Make sure that you collect all the star-shaped yellow color jellyfishes and avoid the blue color dangerous jellyfishes. The colorful graphics, soothing music and easy controls would definitely allow you to keep yourself glued to the screen for hours in this 3D online game. Some different deadly water creatures would try to stop you from moving forward if you come close to them. 
The cool jelly fish movement combined with simple controls will relax your tensed mind and soul. Try to make your jelly fish swim up to screen and make sure that it would not fall down or hit with any obstacles attached with the tree in the deep sea! Good luck to collect all starfishes to complete all missions fast! On atmegame.com, we maintain a huge collection of fish games to play online for free, no download required. Give any of our online games a try to have a blast when you are bored!
